    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Typically used with reference to collectibles and desirable objects not so old as an antique (100 years old), usually reserved for objects dating between the 1940s and 1970s.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
